title: MAR 28 2022 - WAR IN UKRAINE - DAY 33 UPDATE
description:
French President Emmanuel Macron warns against “escalation of words” after President Biden’s speech saying, “Putin cannot remain in power.” Advisor to Ukrainian President Zelensky, Oleksiy Arestovich releases a video reminding soldiers to adhere to the Geneva Convention. Meanwhile, Hunter Biden helped secure funds for U.S. biolab contractors in Ukraine, and Posobiec unpacks Professor Sempa latest Op-Ed, ‘Our Elites Need to Recognize that America’s ‘Unipolar Moment’ is Over.’


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
